quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  23,93,"Yithi: “Nkosi yam ukuba Ungandibonisa oko bathejiswe ngako"
  23,94,Nkosi yam Ungandenzi ndibe kunye nabantu abenza ubugwenxa
  23,95,"Kananjalo inene, Thina Siyakwazi ukukubonisa oko Sibathembise ngako"
  23,96,"Susa (ububi) ngokulungileyo, Thina Sizazi kakuhle izinto (ezingcolileyo) abazithethayo"
  23,97,"Kananjalo yithi: “Nkosi yam! Ndifuna ukhuseleko ngaWe ekungcoleni kokusetyezwa ngamaShayâtîn (ooSathana)"
  23,98,"Ndifuna ukhuseleko kananjalo ngaWe, Nkosi yam! Kuba hleze basondele kum"
  23,99,"De ukufa kufikele omnye wabo (abo bayamanisa amahlulane\tkuAllâh),\taze\t(aqale)\tathi:\t“Nkosi\tyam! Ndibuyisele emva (ebomini)"
  23,100,Khon’ukuze ndiye kwenza okulungileyo koko ndakushiya ngasemva!” Unotshe! Lilizwi nje elo alithethayo; kwaye emva kwabo (abafileyo) kukho iBharzarh (umsantsa) kude kube yiMini abaya kuvuswa ngayo
  23,101,"Ke kaloku lisakuvuthelwa iXilongo, akuyi kubakho kuzalana phakathi kwabo ngaloo Mini, bengayi kubuzana omnye ngomnye"
  23,102,"Abo ke izenzo zabo (ezilungileyo) ziya kubanzima esikalini, ngabaphumeleleyo"
  23,103,"Ke bona abo izenzo zabo ezilungileyo ziya kufumaniseka zilula, ngabo abaya kulahlekelwa yimiphefumlo yabo, esiHogweni kulapho baya kuhlala khona"
  23,104,"UMlilo uya kubatshisa ubuso babo, babe zintlini-ntlini (ezitwezeke imilomo)"
  23,105,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo), “Azanga zicengcelezwe na iiVesi zaM kuni naza nina naziphika?”"
  23,106,"Baya kuthi bona: “Nkosi yethu ukungcola kwethu kwasongamela, inene thina sasingabenzi bobugwenxa"
  23,107,"Nkosi yethu Sikhuphe apha. Ukuba sikhe saphinda sabuyela (ekungcoleni), siya kuba ngokwenene singabenzi bobubi.”"
  23,108,"UAllâh Uya kuthi: “Hlalani apho, nidelekile, ningathethi naM"
  23,109,"Inene kwakukho iqela lezicaka zaM ezaye zathi: ‘Nkosi yethu, thina sikholiwe, sixolele ke ngoko ube nenceba kuthi, yaye Wena Ungoyena Unenceba kwabo banenceba.”"
  23,110,"Kodwa nina nabathatha ngokubagculela nada nafikelela kwinqanaba lokuba banenze nilibale ngenkumbulo yaM, yaye nanidla ngokubahleka nina"
  23,111,"Inene Mna Ndibabuyekezile naMhlanje ngokunyamezela kwabo: inene bona bangabona baphumeleleyo"
  23,112,"Yena (uAllâh) Uya kuthi: “Mingaphi iminyaka enayihlala emhlabeni?”"
  23,113,"Baya kuthi bona: “Sahlala imini enye okanye inxalenye yemini. Buza kwabo babhala phantsi (bagcina iziganeko)"
  23,114,"Yena (uAllâh) Uya kuthi: “Anihlalanga, koko ibe ilixeshana elincinane, ukuba benisazi"
  23,115,"Nanicinga ukuba Sanidalela imfeketho na [Singenanjongo, (nicinga)] nokuba anizi kuphinda nibuyiselwe kwakuThi?”"
  23,116,"Ngoko\tke\tmakaphakanyiswe\tuAllâh, uKumkani wokwenyani: Akakho omnye uthixo ngaphandle kwaKhe, iNkosi yeTrone eNkulu"
  23,117,Nabani na ke obiza komnye uthixo ngaphandle koAllâh angenabungqina ngaye ityala lakhe lowo liseNkosini yakhe. Inene abangakholwayo abayi kuphumelela
  23,118,"Ke wena (Muhammad) yithi: “Nkosi yam, ndixolele Ube nenceba (kum), yaye Wena Ungoyena Unenceba kwabanenceba.”"